    <section class="brand--department-for-business-innovation-skills organisation__margin-bottom" id="org-contacts">
  <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--padding gem-c-heading--border-top-5 brand--department-for-business-innovation-skills brand__border-color">Contact Charity Commission</h2>


    <div class="organisation__contact-section organisation__contact-section--border-top">
    <h3 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--font-size-19 gem-c-heading--padding  ">Contact Centre </h3>


    <div class="grid-row">

        <div class="column-two-thirds">


            <div class="organisation__margin-bottom">
                <p>Open Monday to Friday, 10am to midday and 1pm until 3pm</p>
                <p class="organisation__contact-number">0300 066 9197</p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <p>We cannot talk you through a form or provide password information.<br></br><br></br>Find out how to get a password or log in to Charity Commission online services<br></br><a href="http://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/charity-commission/about-our-services" class="brand__color">www.gov.uk/government/organisations/charity-commission/about-our-services</a><br></br><br></br>Our email addresses have changed, they no longer have '.gsi' in the address. All our email addresses now end with @charitycommission.gov.uk</p>
  </div>
  <div class="organisation__contact-section organisation__contact-section--border-top">
    <h3 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--font-size-19 gem-c-heading--padding  ">Complain about a charity</h3>


    <div class="grid-row">

        <div class="column-two-thirds">

            <div class="organisation__margin-bottom">
                <p><a class="brand__color" href="https://www.gov.uk/complain-about-charity/">Contact Form: Complain about a charity</a></p>
            </div>

            <div class="organisation__margin-bottom">
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <p>What to do if a charity won't deal with your complaint, or if you suspect illegal activity like terrorism or abuse.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="organisation__contact-section organisation__contact-section--border-top">
    <h3 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--font-size-19 gem-c-heading--padding  ">Enquiry form</h3>


    <div class="grid-row">

        <div class="column-two-thirds">

            <div class="organisation__margin-bottom">
                <p><a class="brand__color" href="https://forms.charitycommission.gov.uk/enquiry-form/">Contact Form: Enquiry form</a></p>
            </div>

            <div class="organisation__margin-bottom">
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <p>We can only respond to an enquiry when the Charity Commission has to be involved.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="organisation__contact-section organisation__contact-section--border-top">
    <h3 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--font-size-19 gem-c-heading--padding  ">Report a serious incident in your charity</h3>


    <div class="grid-row">

    </div>
    <p>Charity trustees must report serious incidents to us, and explain how incidents are being dealt with. <br></br><br></br>Find out how to report serious incidents and what to report.<br></br><br></br><a href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/how-to-report-a-serious-incident-in-your-charity" class="brand__color">https://www.gov.uk/guidance/how-to-report-a-serious-incident-in-your-charity</a> <br></br></p>
  </div>
  <div class="organisation__contact-section organisation__contact-section--border-top">
    <h3 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--font-size-19 gem-c-heading--padding  ">Whistleblowing</h3>


    <div class="grid-row">

    </div>
    <p>Find out what sort of wrongdoing you can report to the Charity Commission, and how to report it.<br></br><br></br><a href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/report-serious-wrongdoing-at-a-charity-as-a-worker-or-volunteer" class="brand__color">https://www.gov.uk/guidance/report-serious-wrongdoing-at-a-charity-as-a-worker-or-volunteer</a></p>
  </div>
  <div class="organisation__contact-section organisation__contact-section--border-top">
    <h3 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--font-size-19 gem-c-heading--padding  ">Freedom of Information (FOI) requests</h3>


    <div class="grid-row">

        <div class="column-two-thirds">
            <div class="organisation__margin-bottom">
              <p>Email</p>
                <p><a class="brand__color" href="mailto:FOIrequests@charitycommission.gov.uk">FOIrequests@charitycommission.gov.uk</a></p>
            </div>


            <div class="organisation__margin-bottom">
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <p>Read our privacy notice about how we process your data when you submit a Freedom of Information (FOI) request<br></br><a href="http://www.gov.uk/government/publications/charity-commission-freedom-of-informationenvironmental-information-regulations-request-privacy-notice" class="brand__color">www.gov.uk/government/publications/charity-commission-freedom-of-informationenvironmental-information-regulations-request-privacy-notice</a></p>
